---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro'
import Button from '../../components/common/Button.astro'
---

<Layout
    title="Taxi and transport shift schedules effortlessly | tyovuorolista.fi"
    description="Clear day and night shifts in one tool. Speeds up driver scheduling and ensures personalized schedules. Try for free!"
    ogTitle="Taxi and transport shift schedules effortlessly"
    ogDescription="Irregular working hours? Drag-and-drop makes switching shifts easy. Drivers can belong to multiple teams. Payroll report to Procountor."
    ogUrl="https://tyovuorolista.fi/en/taxi-and-transport"
    ogImage="https://tyovuorolista.fi/assets/metaImage.png"
>
    <div class="landing-wrapper">
        <div class="hero-section">
            <h1>Taxi and transport shift schedules effortlessly</h1>
            <p class="hero-subtitle">Clear day and night shifts in one tool. Työvuorolista speeds up driver scheduling and ensures that everyone gets their personalized schedule.</p>
            
            <div class="video-container">
                <video controls preload="metadata" poster="/tyovuorolista_hero.png">
                    <source src="/blogPostImages/tyovuorolista-demo.webm" type="video/webm" />
                    Your browser doesn't support video.
                </video>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="content-section">
            <div class="problem-solution">
                <h2>Problem and solution</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Irregular working hours? Drag-and-drop makes switching shifts easy.</li>
                    <li>Drivers can belong to multiple teams, e.g. different city areas.</li>
                    <li>Payroll report to Procountor saves on bookkeeping.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="key-features">
                <h2>Key features</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Personalized email lists and PDF images.</li>
                    <li>Calculation of actual hours and overtime warnings.</li>
                    <li>Team-specific calendar and notes e.g. for special assignments.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="resource-scheduling">
                <h2>Vehicle and fleet scheduling</h2>
                <p>The new resource scheduling feature significantly simplifies the management of cars and vans. Link vehicles directly to shifts and the system helps avoid conflicts:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Automatic warnings:</strong> The system warns if a vehicle is already in use at the same time or out of service for maintenance.</li>
                    <li><strong>Default vehicles:</strong> Set default vehicles for employees that are automatically selected for new shifts.</li>
                    <li><strong>Maintenance management:</strong> Mark vehicles as out of service for maintenance, and the system warns if you try to use them.</li>
                    <li><strong>Clarity:</strong> Vehicles automatically appear in shift schedules and emails, so drivers know immediately which vehicle they're using.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="testimonial">
                <h2>Customer experiences</h2>
                <blockquote>
                    "Creating shift schedules has been really easy. Employees also praise the appearance of the schedules!"
                    <cite>– <strong>Laura Dahlman, Restaurant Apaja</strong></cite>
                </blockquote>
            </div>

            <div class="pricing">
                <h2>Pricing</h2>
                <div class="pricing-tiers">
                    <div class="tier">
                        <h3>0 €</h3>
                        <p>3 employees</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="tier">
                        <h3>12 €</h3>
                        <p>20 employees</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="tier">
                        <h3>42 €</h3>
                        <p>50 employees</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="tier">
                        <h3>120 €</h3>
                        <p>over 50 employees (VAT 24%)</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="cta-section">
                <Button
                    text="Try Työvuorolista for free"
                    backgroundColor="var(--tummanvihrea)"
                    textColor="var(--vaaleanharmaa)"
                    href="https://app.tyovuorolista.fi/CreateNewAccount"
                />
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>

<style>
    .landing-wrapper {
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: var(--space-base);
    }

    .hero-section {
        text-align: center;
        padding: var(--space-4xl) 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--vaaleanharmaa);
        margin-bottom: var(--space-4xl);
    }

    h1 {
        font-size: var(--text-4xl);
        color: var(--tummanvihrea);
        margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
        font-weight: 600;
    }

    .hero-subtitle {
        font-size: var(--text-lg);
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: var(--harmaa);
        margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
        max-width: 800px;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
    }

    .hero-cta {
        font-size: var(--text-base);
        color: var(--tummanvihrea);
        margin-bottom: var(--space-4xl);
    }

    .video-container {
        margin: 0 auto;
        max-width: 800px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        border-radius: 12px;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    .video-container video {
        width: 100%;
        height: auto;
        display: block;
    }

    .content-section {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: var(--space-4xl);
    }

    h2 {
        font-size: var(--text-2xl);
        color: var(--tummanvihrea);
        margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
        font-weight: 600;
    }

    ul {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
    }

    li {
        padding: var(--space-sm) 0;
        font-size: var(--text-base);
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: var(--harmaa);
        position: relative;
        padding-left: var(--space-lg);
    }

    li::before {
        content: "✓";
        position: absolute;
        left: 0;
        color: var(--tummanvihrea);
        font-weight: bold;
    }

    .testimonial {
        background-color: var(--vaaleanharmaa);
        padding: var(--space-4xl);
        border-radius: 12px;
        text-align: center;
    }

    blockquote {
        font-size: var(--text-lg);
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: var(--harmaa);
        margin: 0;
        font-style: italic;
    }

    cite {
        display: block;
        margin-top: var(--space-lg);
        font-size: var(--text-base);
        color: var(--tummanvihrea);
        font-style: normal;
    }

    .pricing-tiers {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
        gap: var(--space-lg);
        margin-top: var(--space-lg);
    }

    .tier {
        background-color: white;
        border: 1px solid var(--vaaleanharmaa);
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: var(--space-xl);
        text-align: center;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .tier:hover {
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        box-shadow: 0 6px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .tier h3 {
        font-size: var(--text-2xl);
        color: var(--tummanvihrea);
        margin: 0 0 var(--space-sm) 0;
        font-weight: 600;
    }

    .tier p {
        color: var(--harmaa);
        margin: 0;
    }

    .resource-scheduling {
        background-color: var(--vaaleanharmaa);
        padding: var(--space-4xl);
        border-radius: 12px;
        border: 2px solid var(--tummanvihrea);
    }

    .resource-scheduling p {
        font-size: var(--text-base);
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: var(--harmaa);
        margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    }

    .resource-scheduling ul {
        margin-top: var(--space-lg);
    }

    .resource-scheduling li strong {
        color: var(--tummanvihrea);
        font-weight: 600;
    }

    .cta-section {
        text-align: center;
        padding: var(--space-4xl) 0;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--vaaleanharmaa);
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        h1 {
            font-size: var(--text-3xl);
        }

        .hero-subtitle {
            font-size: var(--text-base);
        }

        .video-container {
            max-width: 100%;
        }

        .content-section {
            gap: var(--space-2xl);
        }

        .testimonial {
            padding: var(--space-2xl);
        }

        .resource-scheduling {
            padding: var(--space-2xl);
        }

        .pricing-tiers {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
    }
</style>

